  "title": "Service Technician | Mechanical Maintenance | Oil & Gas | West",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is from Oil and Gas industry, a local leading player. They are looking for a Maintenance Technician for the next phase of their business. They are located in West.</strong></p><p><strong>Duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform preventive, predictive, and corrective maintenance tasks as directed, and update the CMMS database.</li><li>Maintain rotating and static equipment, plant piping, and structural support systems.</li><li>Respond to and resolve equipment malfunctions, ensuring minimal downtime.</li><li>Determine necessary materials, tools, and methods for safe maintenance tasks.</li><li>Conduct machinery condition monitoring and field data collection with the production team.</li><li>Ensure operational efficiency of all plant valves and mechanical components, including control and plant valve maintenance.</li><li>Supervise in-house contractors and vendors, ensuring safety protocols are followed.</li><li>Collaborate with the production team on mechanical system testing and troubleshooting.</li><li>Participate in the Company's Emergency Response Team (CERT) with assigned roles.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Nitec in Engineering related field.</li><li>Min 5 years’ experience in Oil & Gas or Petrochemical industry</li><li>Experience in troubleshooting of mechanical/ machinery systems</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License No: 19C9682</p><p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
